"title": "6231: rejection of God",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6231: rejection of god",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The deliberate rejection of God lies at the heart of human sin. It is seen in rebellion against God's authority, purpose and instruction and results in the rejection of God's servants and, ultimately, in the rejection of his Son.</p>\n<h2>Rejection of God</h2>\n<h3>Rejection of God's authority</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:15\">2KI 17:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:4\">ISA 1:4</a></p>\n<h3>Rejection of God in favour of other gods</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:15-Deut32:18\">DEU 32:15–32:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:20\">EXO 22:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:20\">DEU 31:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam8:8\">1SA 8:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:28\">ISA 1:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:11\">ISA 65:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:6\">JER 15:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek14:5\">EZK 14:5</a></p>\n<h3>Rejection of God as king</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam8:7\">1SA 8:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:19\">1SA 10:19</a></p>\n<h3>Rejection of God's ways</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps95:10\">PSA 95:10</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:15\">ISA 30:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:7-Exod16:8\">EXO 16:7–16:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:18-Num11:20\">NUM 11:18–11:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:27\">NUM 14:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps81:11-Ps81:13\">PSA 81:11–81:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:6\">ISA 8:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:1-Isa30:2\">ISA 30:1–30:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:30\">LUK 7:30</a></p>\n<h3>Rejection of the covenant</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:10\">1KI 19:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:15\">LEV 26:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:14\">1KI 19:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos8:1\">HOS 8:1</a></p>\n<h3>Rejection of the promised land</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:1-Num14:4\">NUM 14:1–14:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:31\">NUM 14:31</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:30\">NEH 9:30</a></p>\n<h3>Rejection of God's compassion</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:37\">MAT 23:37</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:15\">2CH 36:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:30\">NEH 9:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:1-Hos11:4\">HOS 11:1–11:4</a></p>\n<h2>Rejection of God's word</h2>\n<h3>Rejection of God's instruction</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:10-1Sam15:11\">1SA 15:10–15:11</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:8\">1TH 4:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:23\">1SA 15:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:26\">1SA 15:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps50:17\">PSA 50:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:24-Prov1:25\">PRO 1:24–1:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov5:12\">PRO 5:12</a></p>\n<h3>Rejection of God's law</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:43\">LEV 26:43</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos4:6\">HOS 4:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:26\">2KI 17:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:24\">ISA 5:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:19\">JER 6:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer8:8-Jer8:9\">JER 8:8–8:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek5:6\">EZK 5:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:13\">EZK 20:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:16\">EZK 20:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:24\">EZK 20:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos2:4\">AMO 2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:13\">MRK 7:13</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:6\">MAT 15:6</a></p>\n<h3>Rejection of God's messages</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:12\">ISA 30:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:12\">ISA 65:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:10\">JER 6:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:13\">JER 7:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer35:17\">JER 35:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer36:23-Jer36:24\">JER 36:23–36:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:46\">ACT 13:46</a></p>\n<h3>Rejection of God's messengers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:16\">2CH 36:16</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:52\">ACT 7:52</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr30:10\">2CH 30:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer20:8\">JER 20:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech7:12\">ZEC 7:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:33-Matt21:39\">MAT 21:33–21:39</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:1-Mark12:8\">MRK 12:1–12:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:9-Luke20:15\">LUK 20:9–20:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:35\">ACT 7:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:39\">ACT 7:39</a></p>\n<h2>Rejection of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's rejection was prophesied</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps118:22\">PSA 118:22</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:3\">ISA 53:3</a></strong> <em>It is generally accepted that God's servant in Isaiah chapter 53 refers to Jesus Christ</em>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:31\">MRK 8:31</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:21\">MAT 16:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:22\">LUK 9:22</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:7\">ISA 49:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa50:6\">ISA 50:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:14\">ISA 52:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:7-Isa53:8\">ISA 53:7–53:8</a>MAT <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa21:42\">21:42</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:10\">MRK 12:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke20:17\">LUK 20:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:11\">ACT 4:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:7\">1PE 2:7</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:12\">MRK 9:12</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:12\">MAT 17:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:25\">LUK 17:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:33\">ROM 9:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:16\">ISA 28:16</a></p>\n<h3>The rejection of his earthly ministry</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:11\">JHN 1:11</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:54-Matt13:58\">MAT 13:54–13:58</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:1-Mark6:6\">MRK 6:1–6:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:28-Luke4:29\">LUK 4:28–4:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:40\">JHN 5:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:43\">JHN 5:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:41-John6:42\">JHN 6:41–6:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:59\">JHN 8:59</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:16\">JHN 9:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:31\">JHN 10:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:22-Matt27:23\">MAT 27:22–27:23</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:12-Mark15:14\">MRK 15:12–15:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:20-Luke23:23\">LUK 23:20–23:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:53\">JHN 11:53</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:6\">JHN 19:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:15\">JHN 19:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:23\">ACT 2:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:10\">ACT 4:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:52\">ACT 7:52</a></p>",
